-- Blackberry Said to Keep Pursuing Sale After Securing Financing
-- B y   S e r e n a   S a i t t o
-- 2013-11-04T14:56:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-04/blackberry-said-to-keep-pursuing-sale-after-securing-financing.html
BlackBerry Ltd. will keep pursuing a
sale of the company or units now that it has secured $1 billion
in financing from investors led by  Fairfax Financial Holdings
Ltd. (FFH) , according to people familiar with the situation.  The financing is intended to stabilize BlackBerry as it
burns cash, the people said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
